Usage: commit_module_model [-help] [-copy_mmmc_latencies]
                           [-merged_mmmc_map_file <string>]
                           [-merged_mmmc_sdc_files <string>]
                           [-mmmc_file <string>]
                           [-mmmc_module_model_tag <string>] [-propagate_clocks] [-cpf_file <string> | -1801 <string>]

-help                               # Prints out the command usage
-1801 <string>                      # Specifies ieee 1801 file
                                    # (string, optional)
-copy_mmmc_latencies                # keep MMMC Latencies (bool, optional)
-cpf_file <string>                  # Specifies full chip CPF file to use
                                    # (string, optional)
-merged_mmmc_map_file <string>      # Specifies merge hierarchical mmmc map
                                    # files (string, optional)
-merged_mmmc_sdc_files <string>     # Specifies merged sdc files
                                    # (string, optional)
-mmmc_file <string>                 # Specifies full chip MMMC view file
                                    # (string, optional)
-mmmc_module_model_tag <string>     # Specifies MMMC module model tag
                                    # (string, optional)
-propagate_clocks                   # propagate clocks (bool, optional)